article.headline: Harvey scores 19 as Tennessee Tech takes down Southeast Missouri State 70-59
article.description: — Jayvis Harvey had 19 points in Tennessee Tech's 70-59 win over Southeast Missouri State on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Harvey scores 19 as Tennessee Tech takes down Southeast Missouri State 70-59
article.story: COOKEVILLE, Tenn. -- — Jayvis Harvey had 19 points in Tennessee Tech's 70-59 win over Southeast Missouri State on Saturday night. Harvey added three steals for the Golden Eagles (7-11, 2/3 Ohio Valley Conference). Daniel Egbuniwe scored 14 points and added 10 rebounds and five assists. Diante Wood and Josiah Davis added 13 points apiece. The Redhawks (6-12, 1-4) were led by Josh Earley, who recorded 20 points. Rob Martin added 12 points for Southeast Missouri State. TJ Biel also had eight points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
